In http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/CONF-9193 we discussed that it might be good to have some sort of utility (a link in a Confluence page) that could copy all of the comments from a page into a forum. This would be useful for pages that have lots of comments hosted by Atlassian to move those comments into either their own forum or forum thread (depending on what was more applicable).

This might make for a great ShipIt day project for someone! :) But, it might also be a good built-in feature.

